          <p class="text-[#8b949e] text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Game of Tell: two-player card game with synchronized face video and remote PPG.
            Analyzing facial AUs, head pose, gaze, and physiological synchrony between dyads.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-1">
            <span class="tag">rPPG</span><span class="tag">OpenFace</span><span class="tag">Synchrony</span>
          </div>
